  "title": "Business Analyst (Insurance / Agile)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Business Analyst (Insurance / Agile)</strong></p><p><strong>Role:</strong> Senior Business Analyst – Insurance<br /><br /><strong>Role Overview</strong></p><p>Drive business requirements and delivery alignment for insurance digital transformation programs. Bridge business stakeholders and Agile delivery teams.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Gather and document business requirements and user stories.</li><li>Facilitate workshops, process mapping, gap analysis.</li><li>Support backlog grooming, sprint planning, UAT.</li><li>Coordinate with Product Owners, Developers, QA.</li><li>Ensure regulatory and operational compliance.</li><li>Support go-live and change management.</li></ul><p><strong>Mandatory Skills</strong></p><ul><li>5+ years Business Analysis in Insurance.</li><li>Strong knowledge of policy lifecycle, claims, billing.</li><li>Agile / Scrum delivery experience.</li><li>Excellent stakeholder management and documentation skills.</li><li>Insurance Policy Admin System (PAS) exposure.</li><li>Tools: Jira, Confluence, Visio.</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred</strong></p><ul><li>API / digital platform understanding.</li><li>MAS / compliance familiarity.</li></ul>",
